{{Youmay|the lead ship of the ''Aramadia''-class, the ''Aramadia''|the [[Aramadia-class thrustship|''Aramadia''-class thrustship]] or the [[Super Star Destroyer/Legends|Super Star Destroyer]] [[Aramadia (Super Star Destroyer)|''Aramadia'']]}}
The '''''Aramadia''''' was an [[Aramadia-class thrustship|''Aramadia''-class thrustship]].

==History==
The lead ship of the ''Aramadia'' class, it was chosen by [[Nil Spaar]] as his diplomatic vessel. When ''Aramadia'' traveled to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] to begin Nil Spaar's diversionary talks with the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], military and intelligence officers spent hours pouring over scans and [[Hologram/Legends|holos]] of ''Aramadia'' to gain an understanding of [[Yevetha]]n technology.

